{"tid":1795233,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"屌哂你地老母，好心你地咪撚再去錯啦","createTime":"2019-12-23T17:31:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-26T18:52:13.000Z","uid":28921,"like":597,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":87,"replies":[{"pid":"c298b56abe9f29505e2a1315d866897bf88fc670","tid":1795233,"uid":28921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T17:31:40.000Z","msg":"你班友仔睇完高登直播去太安樓食雜炒，好心咪撚再去藍店啦<br />\n<br />\n近大家樂果間係藍店，係。藍。店！<br />\n<br />\n屌哂你地班on9仔！！！！！！！<br />\n人地藍到發紫，仲on9送錢俾人！！！！<br />\n仲排長龍！<br />\n<br />\n仲叫個啊姐唔使找錢，乜撚野事，係咪請啲狗食野？<br />\n呢間野見撚到黑警，收少幾蚊之餘仲加隻蛋俾佢啊！<br />\n你地好撚多錢都唔使請黑警食野啊嘛，行遠少少捐去魚蛋佬啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有啲山長水遠去太安樓食，食藍店，你地無撚野啊！！！！！！！<br />\n<br />\n對高登食果間雜炒有保留，但都要講返個真正地址，係影印舖對面。<br />\n<br />\n利申，西灣河街坊"},{"pid":"a82a43ea1bba4941795036928ec5d7d43efc9639","tid":1795233,"uid":70888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T17:39:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9eea17755585e68ec5c4a322129f8510e41f71fb","tid":1795233,"uid":258683,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T17:39:59.000Z","msg":"屌唔係呀嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />益撚曬人"},{"pid":"6d55ce2631f3312dfd6307ce358afb8caacf42a9","tid":1795233,"uid":53062,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T17:41:15.000Z","msg":"笑咗，送錢俾對家"},{"pid":"664d93e93f3865e9754b2f659ac93e9ca29666c4","tid":1795233,"uid":142383,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T17:50:38.000Z","msg":"開名啦"},{"p